&lt;p&gt;This is a hands-on builder role on a small, high-leverage team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Pinwheel is a hybrid environment, with a 3-day in-office requirement here in our NYC headquarters, near Union Square.&lt;/p&gt;
